===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Sabrina (Masters)}}
Sabrina, in her {{game|FireRed and LeafGreen|s}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Alakazam}} and {{p|Chingling}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Alakazam is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. As Bellelba, Sabrina forms a sync pair with {{p|Swoobat}}. Sabrina became a playable sync pair on March 16, 2020, with her appearing as Bellelba on May 2, 2024.

